    note absent in hive/tool — must cross-repo import or duplicate topo+cycle helpers
  raw-80-sentinel
    pattern __BLOCKER_FANOUT_RESULT__ PASS|FAIL slug=<slug> n=N ok=K agg=<mode>
    consumer downstream omega-cycle convergence + atlas append
  raw-77-audit-ledger
